        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/780616195/O1CN013lM3ke1vdMFctI2zV_!!780616195.png_240x240.jpg"></p><hr><table><thead><tr><th>A</th><th>B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/780616195/O1CN01T2MsON1vdMFVmyWGD_!!780616195.jpg_240x240.jpg"></td><td><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/780616195/O1CN018tKRrw1vdMFgqEn65_!!780616195.jpg_240x240.jpg"></td></tr><tr><td>_1</td><td>_2</td></tr><tr><td><img src="https://fly-52elong-bf.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/yifang/yifang_%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83/IMG_20170307_100659.jpg"></td><td><img src="https://fly-52elong-bf.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/yifang/yifang_%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83/IMG_20170307_101016.jpg"></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><p>HarmonyOS是一款“面向未来”、面向全场景（移动办公、运动健康、社交通信、媒体娱乐等）的分布式操作系统。在传统的单设备系统能力的基础上，HarmonyOS提出了基于同一套系统能力、适配多种终端形态的分布式理念，能够支持多种终端设备.</p><h2 id="通知类"><a href="#通知类" class="headerlink" title="通知类"></a>通知类</h2><h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201127130343188.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTI1Mjk4NjA=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70"></h2><p>GG</p><hr><script async="" src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script><p><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block; text-align:center;" data-ad-layout="in-article" data-ad-format="fluid" data-ad-client="ca-pub-7237853059527557" data-ad-slot="7212808246"></ins></p><script>     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script><hr>]]></content>
      
      
